Home cooked & handmade, a revolutionary pet food for busy pet parents who want to feed fresh!

  • Nutritionist formulated and vet recommended - a natural and delicious Chicken recipe for better and longer life
  • Preservative-free, Ready-to-Serve Wet Dog Food. No cooking or refrigeration required.
  • With Chicken as #1 ingredient, this high protein recipe has all the essential amino acids your dog needs.
  • Promotes strong muscles and bones. Improves skin and fur quality.
  • Reduces allergies, builds immunity and improves gut health.

Ingredients

Whole Chicken, Rice, Eggs, Pumpkin, Carrot, Beans, Chicken Liver, Apple Sauce, Chia Seeds, Cold Pressed Coconut Oil, Flax Seeds, Flax Seed Oil, Fresh Mint, Egg Shell Powder, Organic Turmeric, Ashwagandha, Moringa, Mixed Herbs

How To Use

Meals are ready to serve. Simply cut and pour into your dog's feeding bowl. To serve warm meals, put pack in the microwave for 2 min or dip packs in hot water for 5 min.

Storage Guide

No refrigeration required. Meals are packed using the latest Retort technology and retain freshness and nutrient value for upto 2 year without using any preservatives. Store unopened packs in a cool and dry place, away from direct sunlight. Once opened, refrigerate unused meal and use within 24 hours.

Estimated Delivery Time

1-3 days in Delhi NCR

3-7 days in Rest of India

Some Frequently Asked Questions

If there are no preservatives then how do the meals remain fresh?

Meals are packed using the latest packaging technology (the same that was introduced by NASA for their astronauts). With the help of this technology, we are able to maintain the freshness and nutrient value of our meals for a longer time.

How is FurrMeals different from other dog food?

At FurrMeals, we don’t make dog food, instead we make food for dogs. Our meals are made with high-quality, human-grade, whole food ingredients, which are more bio-available than fillers and other low-quality ingredients. We prep and cook our meals in human-grade kitchen, the same way human food is made. Every meal is hot-filled to ensure safety and retort packed to lock in freshness and nutrient value.

How to store the FurrMeals meal packs?

FurrMeals packs can be stored in any cupboard or counter, that is away from direct sunlight. Store in a cool and dry place.

Can I order a sample to start before going for a plan?

Start with a Trial Pack or a Combo Plan that has mix of recipes. Once your dog has tried the food, you can choose a plan that best suits the taste of your doggo.

How do I transition my pup to FurrMeals?

Start by mixing FurrMeals in with your pup's current food.

Day 1-2 : 25% FurrMeals 75% Current Food

Day 3-4 : 50% FurrMeals 75% Current Foodof their meal for the firts 2 days. Make it 50% Slowly increase this amount until your dog is eating 100% PetPlate. If your dog has a sensitive stomach or experiences minor tummy trouble, feed a smaller amount and slowly increase until they adjust to their new food.
